name: ωCPO.coe_of
initialProofState:
α : Type u_1
inst✝ : OmegaCompletePartialOrder α
⊢ Eq (↑(ωCPO.of α)) α
decl:
@[simp]
theorem coe_of (α : Type*) [OmegaCompletePartialOrder α] : ↥(of α) = α :=
  rfl

name: ωCPO.HasProducts.instHasProduct
initialProofState:
J : Type v
f : J → ωCPO
⊢ CategoryTheory.Limits.HasProduct f
decl:
instance (J : Type v) (f : J → ωCPO.{v}) : HasProduct f :=
  HasLimit.mk ⟨_, isProduct _ f⟩

name: ωCPO.instHasProducts
decl:
instance : HasProducts.{v} ωCPO.{v} :=
  fun _ => { has_limit := fun _ => hasLimitOfIso Discrete.natIsoFunctor.symm }

name: ωCPO.instHasLimitWalkingParallelPairParallelPair
initialProofState:
X Y : ωCPO
f g : Quiver.Hom X Y
⊢ CategoryTheory.Limits.HasLimit (CategoryTheory.Limits.parallelPair f g)
decl:
instance {X Y : ωCPO.{v}} (f g : X ⟶ Y) : HasLimit (parallelPair f g) :=
  HasLimit.mk ⟨_, HasEqualizers.isEqualizer f g⟩
